source.name: Consolidated Federal Funds Report
source.description: Data on federal government expenditures or obligations in state, county, and subcounty areas of the United States, including the District of Columbia and U.S. Outlying Areas.  It contains statistics on the geographic distribution of federal program expenditures, using data submitted by federal departments and agencies.
